metadata.description: The most epic Wonderland tale begins here. Alice Liddle is no longer the little girl you once knew. Years have passed since she took the trip down the rabbit hole into Wonderland. A grown woman now with a husband and kids of her own, Alice has everything a person could want. But all is not right with Alice. Not right at all. Now Alice's daughter Carroll Ann will be forced to take a journey not for the faint of heart, a journey into the realm of madness and into a place where the adventures of Alice were only the beginning. You've never seen Wonderland quite like this.
metadata.name: Return To Wonderland
